ction Results</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600\">Detailed results by district, office, and vote type</p></a><a class=\"block p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 shadow-sm hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-md transition-all focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2\" href=\"/poll-sites\"><h3 class=\"font-medium text-primary-700\">View Poll Sites</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600\">Election Day and Early Voting locations</p></a><a class=\"block p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 shadow-sm hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-md transition-all focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2\" href=\"/compliance\"><h3 class=\"font-medium text-primary-700\">View Compliance Reports</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600\">Semi-annual non-compliance reports</p></a><a class=\"block p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 shadow-sm hover:border-primary-300 hover:shadow-md transition-all focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2\" href=\"/downloads\"><h3 class=\"font-medium text-primary-700\">Download Data</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-600\">Export data in CSV or JSON</p></a></div></section><section class=\"mt-8\" aria-label=\"Recent Elections\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4\">Recent Elections</h2><div class=\"overflow-x-auto border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg\"><table class=\"min-w-full divide-y divide-neutral-200\"><caption class=\"sr-only\">List of recent elections in New York State</caption><thead class=\"bg-neutral-50\"><tr><th scope=\"col\" class=\"px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-600 uppercase\">Election Name</th><th scope=\"col\" class=\"px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-600 uppercase\">Type</th><th scope=\"col\" class=\"px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-600 uppercase\">contests</th></tr></thead><tbody c