\\"Download election data in CSV, JSON, or PDF format\\\",\\\"subtitleShort\\\":\\\"Download election data in CSV or JSON format\\\",\\\"selectCategory\\\":\\\"Select Data Category\\\",\\\"selectFormat\\\":\\\"Select Format\\\",\\\"electionResults\\\":\\\"Election Results\\\",\\\"pollSiteData\\\":\\\"Poll Site Data\\\",\\\"voterStatistics\\\":\\\"Voter Statistics\\\",\\\"invalidAffidavits\\\":\\\"Invalid Affidavits\\\",\\\"startDownload\\\":\\\"Start Download\\\",\\\"downloadNote\\\":\\\"All data excludes personally identifiable information (PII) in accordance with applicable privacy regulations.\\\",\\\"largeFileWarning\\\":\\\"Large datasets may take several seconds to generate.\\\",\\\"allElections\\\":\\\"All Elections\\\",\\\"allMunicipalities\\\":\\\"All Municipalities\\\",\\\"preparing\\\":\\\"Preparing Download...\\\",\\\"aboutDownloads\\\":\\\"About Data Downloads\\\",\\\"dataPrivacy\\\":\\\"Data Privacy Notice\\\",\\\"dataPrivacyText\\\":\\\"All data excludes personally identifiable information (PII) in accordance with applicable privacy regulations. Individual voter records are never included. Voter statistics contain only aggregated counts.\\\",\\\"officialData\\\":\\\"Downloads are generated from official NYS Board of Elections data. Large datasets may take several seconds to generate.\\\",\\\"availableCategories\\\":\\\"Available Data Categories\\\",\\\"exportFormats\\\":\\\"Export Formats\\\",\\\"csvDescription\\\":\\\"Comma-separated values, compatible with Excel and spreadsheet applications\\\",\\\"jsonDescription\\\":\\\"Structured data format for programmatic access and analysis\\\",\\\"downloadFailed\\\":\\\"Download failed. Please try again.\\\",\\\"resultsDesc\\\":\\\"Vote counts by candidate, office, and district\\\",\\\"pollSitesDesc\\\":\\\"Election Day and Early Voting site locations\\\",\\\"voterStatsDesc\\\":\\\"Aggregated voter participation statistics by voting method (no individual records)\\\",\\\"invalidAffidavitsDesc\\\":\\\"Invalid affidavit ballot counts by reason and district\\\",\\\"electionRequired\\\":\\\"Please select an election for this category.\\\",\\\"votingMethod\\\":\\\"Voting Method\\\",\\\"voterCount\\\":\\\"Voter Count\\\",\\\"address1\\\":\\\"Address 1\\\",\\\"address2\\\":\\\"Address 2\\\",\\\"electionDistrictCombinedInto\\\":\\\"Election District Combined Into\\\",\\\"notRegistered\\\":\\\"Not Registered\\\",\\\"movedWithinState\\\":\\\"Moved Within State\\\",\\\"wrongPollingPlace\\\":\\\"Wrong Polling Place\\\",\\\"signatureIssue\\\":\\\"Signature Issue\\\",\\\"alreadyVoted\\\":\\\"Already Voted\\\",\\\"prevAbsentEarlyMailBallot\\\":\\\"Previous Absent/Early Mail Ballot\\\",\\\"incompleteAffidavit\\\":\\\"Incomplete Affidavit\\\",\\\"partyEnrollmentIssue\\\":\\\"Party Enrollment Issue\\\",\\\"other\\\":\\\"Other\\\",\\\"totalInvalid\\\":\\\"Total Invalid\\\",\\\"votingMethod_atPollSite\\\":\\\"At Poll Site\\\",\\\"votingMethod_absentee\\\":\\\"Absentee\\\",\\\"votingMethod_affidavit\\\":\\\"Affidavit\\\",\\\"votingMethod_other\\\":\\\"Other\\\",\\\"votingMethod_earlyVotingAtPollSite\\\":\\\"Early Voting at Poll Site\\\",\\\"votingMethod_earlyVotingByAffidavit\\\":\\\"Early Voting by Affidavit\\\",\\\"votingMethod_earlyVotingByOtherMethod\\\":\\\"Early Voting by Other Method\\\",\\\"header_electionName\\\":\\\"Election Name\\\",\\\"header_contestJurisdiction\\\":\\\"Contest Jurisdiction\\\",\\\"header_contestType\\\":\\\"Contest Type\\\",\\\"header_office\\\":\\\"Office\\\",\\\"header_districtType\\\":\\\"District Type\\\",\\\"header_district\\\":\\\"District\\\",\\\"header_candidate\\\":\\\"Candidate\\\",\\\"header_party\\\":\\\"Party\\\",\\\"header_electionDayVotes\\\":\\\"Election Day Votes\\\",\\\"header_earlyVotes\\\":\\\"Early Votes\\\",\\\"header_votesByMail\\\":\\\"Votes by Mail\\\",\\\"header_affidavitVotes\\\":\\\"Affidavit Votes\\\",\\\"header_voteTotal\\\":\\\"Vote Total\\\",\\\"header_certifiedResult\\\":\\\"Certified Result\\\",\\\"header_pollSiteName\\\":\\\"Poll Site Name\\\",\\\"header_ward\\\":\\\"Ward\\\",\\\"header_precinct\\\":\\\"Precinct\\\",\\\"header_city\\\":\\\"City\\\",\\\"header_state\\\":\\\"State\\\",\\\"header_zip\\\":\\\"ZIP\\\",\\\"header_designation\\\":\\\"Designation\\\"},\\\"compliance\\\":{\\\"title\\\":\\\"Compliance Reports\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"Semi-annual non-compliance reports per NYS Election Law § 3-112 ¶4\\\",\\\"comingSoon\\\":\\\"There is currently no compliance data to display.\\\",\\\"comingSoonDescription\\\":\\\"Compliance report data is not due until January 1, 2027. Once reports are received, they will be published here in accordance with NYS Election Law § 3-112 ¶4.\\\",\\\"authorityName\\\":\\\"Authority Name\\\",\\\"missingDataset\\\":\\\"Missing Dataset\\\",\\\"deadline\\\":\\\"Deadline\\\",\\\"cureDeadline\\\":\\\"Cure Deadline\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"Status\\\",\\\"nonCompliant\\\":\\\"Non-Compliant\\\",\\\"cured\\\":\\\"Cured\\\",\\\"pending\\\":\\\"Pending\\\",\\\"electionDate\\\":\\\"Election Date\\\",\\\"reportDate\\\":\\\"Report Date\\\",\\\"publicationDate\\\":\\\"Publication Date\\\",\\\"effectivePeriod\\\":\\\"Effective Period\\\",\\\"currentReport\\\":\\\"Current Report\\\",\\\"archivedReports\\\":\\\"Archived Reports\\\",\\\"reportPeriod\\\":\\\"Report Period\\\",\\\"allReports\\\":\\\"All Reports\\\",\\\"reportOf\\\":\\\"Report of {date}\\\",\\\"totalRecords\\\":\\\"Total Records\\\",\\\"loadingRecords\\\":\\\"Loading compliance records...\\\",\\\"records\\\":\\\"records\\\",\\\"legalNote\\\":\\\"Compliance reports are published semi-annually per NYS Election Law § 3-112 ¶4. County boards of elections that fail to submit required data by the deadline are listed as non-compliant. A 10 business day cure period is provided before final publication.\\\",\\\"searchPlaceholder\\\":\\\"Search by authority name...\\\",\\\"caption\\\":\\\"Compliance reports showing non-compliant authorities, missing datasets, and cure status\\\",\\\"complianceStats\\\":\\\"Compliance statistics\\\"},\\\"about\\\":{\\\"title\\\":\\\"About Flateau Database\\\",\\\"mission\\\":\\\"Mission\\\",\\\"missionText\\\":\\\"The Voter Election Data Access (VEDA) Election Explorer provides the public with transparent access to New York State election data, as mandated by NYS Election Law § 3-112. This platform publishes curated, non-personally-identifiable election data for public review, research, and oversight.\\\",\\\"accessibility\\\":\\\"Accessibility Statement\\\",\\\"accessibilityText\\\":\\\"The NYS Board of Elections is committed to ensuring that all users can access election data regardless of ability. This application conforms to Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1 Level AA standards.\\\",\\\"accessibilityFeatures\\\":\\\"Accessibility Features\\\",\\\"keyboardNav\\\":\\\"Full keyboard navigation support\\\",\\\"keyboardNavFull\\\":\\\"Full keyboard navigation support for all interactive elements\\\",\\\"screenReader\\\":\\\"Screen reader compatibility\\\",\\\"screenReaderFull\\\":\\\"Screen reader compatibility with ARIA labels and landmarks\\\",\\\"colorContrast\\\":\\\"WCAG AA color contrast compliance\\\",\\\"colorContrastFull\\\":\\\"WCAG 2.1 Level AA color contrast compliance (4.5:1 for normal text, 3:1 for large text)\\\",\\\"textAlternatives\\\":\\\"Text alternatives for all visual content\\\",\\\"textAlternativesFull\\\":\\\"Text alternatives for all charts and visual content\\\",\\\"responsiveDesign\\\":\\\"Responsive design for all devices\\\",\\\"responsiveDesignFull\\\":\\\"Responsive design supporting all devices and screen sizes\\\",\\\"languageSupport\\\":\\\"Multi-language support (14 languages)\\\",\\\"languageSupportFull\\\":\\\"Multi-language support for 14 languages including RTL scripts\\\",\\\"focusIndicators\\\":\\\"Visible focus indicators on all interactive controls\\\",\\\"skipNavigation\\\":\\\"Skip navigation link for keyboard users\\\",\\\"structuredTables\\\":\\\"Properly structured data tables with column headers\\\",\\\"noColorOnly\\\":\\\"No reliance on color alone to convey information\\\",\\\"supportedLanguages\\\":\\\"Supported Languages\\\",\\\"contact\\\":\\\"Contact\\\",\\\"contactText\\\":\\\"For questions about the data or this application, contact the NYS Board of Elections.\\\",\\\"contactFullText\\\":\\\"For questions about the data or this application, contact the NYS Board of Elections at (518) 474-6220 or visit the office at 40 North Pearl Street, Suite 5, Albany, NY 12207-2729.\\\",\\\"dataSource\\\":\\\"Data Source\\\",\\\"dataSourceText\\\":\\\"All data is sourced from official NYS Board of Elections records. Individual voter records are excluded. Only aggregated, public-facing data is presented.\\\",\\\"dataSourceTextFull\\\":\\\"All data is sourced from official NYS Board of Elections records. Individual voter records are excluded. Only aggregated, public-facing data is presented. Data is published after certification by the appropriate election authority.\\\",\\\"legalBasis\\\":\\\"Legal Basis\\\",\\\"legalBasisText\\\":\\\"This application is mandated by NYS Election Law § 3-112, which requires the State Board of Elections to publish election records for public access.\\\",\\\"legalBasisTextFull\\\":\\\"This application is mandated by NYS Election Law § 3-112, which requires the State Board of Elections to publish election records for public access. The statute specifies requirements for data publication including election results at the election district level, poll site information, district boundary data, and semi-annual compliance reporting.\\\",\\\"reportIssue\\\":\\\"Report an Accessibility Issue\\\",\\\"reportIssueDesc\\\":\\\"If you encounter an accessibility barrier while using this application, please contact us so we can address the issue promptly.\\\",\\\"availableData\\\":\\\"Available Data\\\",\\\"electionResultsTitle\\\":\\\"Election Results\\\",\\\"electionResultsDesc\\\":\\\"Vote counts by candidate, office, district, and vote type with certified results\\\",\\\"pollSitesTitle\\\":\\\"Poll Sites\\\",\\\"pollSitesDesc\\\":\\\"Election Day and Early Voting site locations with designations\\\",\\\"districtMapsTitle\\\":\\\"District Maps\\\",\\\"districtMapsDesc\\\":\\\"Interactive boundary maps for congressional, state senate, assembly, and other districts\\\",\\\"voterTurnoutTitle\\\":\\\"Voter Statistics\\\",\\\"voterTurnoutDesc\\\":\\\"Aggregated voter participation by district and voting method\\\",\\\"invalidAffidavitsTitle\\\":\\\"Invalid Affidavits\\\",\\\"invalidAffidavitsDesc\\\":\\\"Invalid affidavit ballot counts by reason and district\\\",\\\"complianceTitle\\\":\\\"Compliance Reports\\\",\\\"complianceDesc\\\":\\\"Semi-annual non-compliance reports for county boards of elections (coming soon)\\\",\\\"contactName\\\":\\\"NYS Board of Elections\\\",\\\"phone\\\":\\\"Phone\\\",\\\"email\\\":\\\"Email\\\",\\\"ballotTabulationsTitle\\\":\\\"Ballot Tabulations\\\",\\\"ballotTabulationsDesc\\\":\\\"Absentee and affidavit ballot counts with validity information\\\"},\\\"dataValues\\\":{\\\"voteTypeElectionDay\\\":\\\"Election Day\\\",\\\"voteTypeEarlyVoting\\\":\\\"Early Voting\\\",\\\"voteTypeByMail\\\":\\\"By Mail\\\",\\\"voteTypeAffidavit\\\":\\\"Affidavit\\\",\\\"voteTypeAtPollSite\\\":\\\"At Poll Site\\\",\\\"voteTypeAbsentee\\\":\\\"Absentee\\\",\\\"voteTypeOther\\\":\\\"Other\\\",\\\"voteTypeEarlyAffidavit\\\":\\\"Early Affidavit\\\",\\\"voteTypeEarlyOther\\\":\\\"Early Other\\\",\\\"jurisdictionFederal\\\":\\\"Federal\\\",\\\"jurisdictionState\\\":\\\"State\\\",\\\"jurisdictionLocal\\\":\\\"Local\\\",\\\"jurisdictionCounty\\\":\\\"County\\\",\\\"jurisdictionSchool\\\":\\\"School\\\",\\\"jurisdictionLibrary\\\":\\\"Library\\\",\\\"districtTypeAssembly\\\":\\\"Assembly\\\",\\\"districtTypeSenate\\\":\\\"Senate\\\",\\\"districtTypeCongressional\\\":\\\"Congressional\\\",\\\"districtTypeStatewide\\\":\\\"Statewide\\\",\\\"districtTypeWard\\\":\\\"Ward\\\",\\\"districtTypePrecinct\\\"